2.10	Chojn%C3%B3w	Chojnów	Chojnów is located 18 km (11 mi) west of Legnica, 26 km (16 mi) east from Bolesławiec and 18 km (11 mi) north of Złotoryja, 5 km (3.1 mi) from the A4 motorway. It has railroad connections to Bolesławiec and Legnica.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/00/Chojnow_001_ratusz.jpg/250px-Chojnow_001_ratusz.jpg
